snippet.title: Survived By - Teaser Trailer - Now in Closed Beta
snippet.description: Permadeath is just the beginning. Human Head and Digital Extremes present Survived By, a ruined world where you and other survivors take on vicious Chimera in order to live. Explore, craft, and loot in this roguelite bullet-hell MMO developed by Human Head Studios. Visit https://www.survivedby.com for more info!
